quires BTC net **>$15M**. Reclaim to bullish requires BTC net **>$17M** plus anchor rebuild. Keep ETH/SOL/HYPE bearish confidence high. Keep PM weekend block active; no Sunday exception. Keep HL live notional-blocked; no forced trades from `$37.39`.\n\n**Next:** Watch whether `anon-0x8fcc` adds to the BTC short or exits. If BTC net remains below `$10M`, maintain hard defensive posture regardless of P4 microstructure.\n\n## 2026-05-03 21:23 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] Range expansion high compression, P1 hardline near\n\n**Task:** Refresh P4 alpha after normalized RANGE/UP continued but P1 defensive overlay remained active, testing whether compression spikes above 1.15 or fast regime turns TREND.\n\n**Finding:**\n- Both bots are alive (`pm-bot`, `hl-bot`).\n- Rotation pointed to **P4**.\n- Ran fresh `/home/ubuntu/clawd/scripts/alpha-signal-update.sh`.\n- Current alpha timestamp: **2026-05-03T21:23:21.570519+00:00**.\n- BTC price **$78,967.64**, 24h **+0.634%**; Fear & Greed **47 Neutral**.\n- Alpha schema drift persists: `regime_state` is raw **RANGE*",
